Package ohos.ivihardware.tbox.model

Class TBoxSubscription

  • java.lang.Object
    • ohos.ivihardware.tbox.model.TBoxSubscription

  • public class TBoxSubscription
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents the subscription descriptor.

    Each subscription descriptor contains the ID and subscription period of a T-Box signal. Once the subscription is successful, a TBoxSubscription object is returned. You can unsubscribe from the specific T-Box signal based on the returned object.

    Since:
    3

    • Constructor Detail

      • TBoxSubscription

        public TBoxSubscription​(java.lang.String propertyId,
                        long interval)
        A constructor used to create a TBoxSubscription instance based on the ID and subscription period of the specified T-Box signal.

        This method may change the subscription period (specified by interval) for periodic subscription. Specifically, the input value of interval is rounded up to a positive integer multiple of 200. For example, if the input value is 0, the actual subscription period will be 200 ms; if the input value is 201, the actual subscription period will be 400 ms.

        Parameters:
        propertyId - Identifies the subscribed T-Box signal.
        interval - Indicates the subscription period.
        Since:
        3

      • getActualInterval

        public long getActualInterval​()
        Obtains the actual subscription period.

        The actual subscription period may be different from the value of interval passed to TBoxManager.subscribeProperty(java.lang.String, ohos.ivihardware.tbox.model.TBoxPropertyCallback, long) and TBoxManager.subscribeBatchProperties(java.util.List<java.lang.String>, ohos.ivihardware.tbox.model.TBoxPropertyCallback, long)

        For example, if the value is 0, the actual subscription period will be 200 ms; if the value is 201, the actual subscription period will be 400 ms; if the value is Long.MAX_VALUE, the actual subscription period will be the same.

        Returns:
        Returns the actual subscription period.
        Since:
        3
